title: Rachel & Becca Answer Your Questions
description:
They've asked for questions and comments every week, and now Becca and Rachel are answering fan questions. Where do they think they would be now if they hadn’t gone on "The Bachelor" and become the Bachelorette? Who would be their dream guests?

Plus, Becca and Rachel play a hilarious game of Never Have I Ever.

Don’t forget to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
